episodes.title: Its Me, Tinx Live: My Friend Joined a Cult
episodes.description: Another week, another first. I talk to a caller who had to drop a lifelong friend due to joining what she views as a cult. A woman who has some serious red flags to deal with in regards to a boyfriend that seems to be angry about nothing. Oh, and when is the best time to sleep with someone new after a long term relationship? Spoiler alert, whenever, wherever, and however you want!
